# HELP replicaset_controller_sorting_deletion_age_ratio [ALPHA] The ratio of chosen deleted pod's ages to the current youngest pod's age (at the time). Should be <2. The intent of this metric is to measure the rough efficacy of the LogarithmicScaleDown feature gate's effect on the sorting (and deletion) of pods when a replicaset scales down. This only considers Ready pods when calculating and reporting.
